=== System Health Provider ===

This provider checks a number of key system performance parameters and raises events if thresholds are exceeded.
Use the checkboxes to activate a given check (e.g. checking for high disk latency). 
The checks create events which can be viewed here [[Admin:Events]].
You can also define a person to be notified via mail. Use the [[Help:EventTrigger]] to do so.
Note that you need to setup your mail server here [[Setup:Email]].
You can also define other tasks to be executed in case of an event. Please see [[Help:Tasks]] for more information.

